#

Mexican Bean and Ground Meat Skillet

30 min
$10
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Quick MealOne-PanMexicanFamily-Friendly

Description

A one-pan dish packed with flavorful ground meat, beans, and zesty spices, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner!

Ingredients

  • ground beef or turkey: 1 lb
  • canned black beans: 15 oz
  • canned diced tomatoes: 15 oz
  • onion, chopped: 1 medium
  • bell pepper, chopped: 1
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • taco seasoning: 1 packet
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • cheddar cheese, shredded: 1 cup
  • fresh cilantro, chopped (optional): for garnish
